"Upon opening the :menuselection:`Discuss app`, the :guilabel:`Discuss` "
"dashboard appears."
msgstr ""
"開啟\\ :menuselection:`聊天應用程式`\\ 後，會顯示\\ :guilabel:`聊天`\\ 儀表"
"板。"

