#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/call_queues.rst:62
msgid "Agent connects to the queue in Odoo, via the **VoIP** widget."
msgstr "代理透過\\ **VoIP**\\ 小工具在 Odoo 中連線到隊列。"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/call_queues.rst:65
