"在從 Odoo 樞紐分析檢視插入的靜態樞紐分析表中，如有需要，請手動刪除第二個頁首"
"列。"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/spreadsheet/work_with_data/pivot_tables.rst:477
msgid "Duplicate or delete a pivot table"
msgstr "複製或刪除樞紐分析表"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/spreadsheet/work_with_data/pivot_tables.rst:480
msgid ""
"When :ref:`duplicating <spreadsheet/pivot-tables/duplicate>` "
"or :ref:`deleting <spreadsheet/pivot-tables/delete>` a pivot table, it is "
"important to remember that each inserted pivot table also has a :ref:`data "
"source <spreadsheet/insert/data-sources>`."
msgstr ""
":ref:`複製 <spreadsheet/pivot-tables/duplicate>`\\ 或\\ :ref:`刪除 "
"<spreadsheet/pivot-tables/delete>`\\ 樞紐分析表時，請務必記住每個插入的樞紐分"
"析表也都有一個\\ :ref:`資料來源 <spreadsheet/insert/data-sources>`\\ 。"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/spreadsheet/work_with_data/pivot_tables.rst:487
msgid "Duplicate a pivot table"
msgstr "複製樞紐分析表"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/spreadsheet/work_with_data/pivot_tables.rst:489
msgid ""
"Duplicating a pivot table via the pivot table's properties creates an "
"additional data source. This allows for different manipulations to be "
"performed on the same data within one spreadsheet. For example, you can see "
"the same data aggregated by different dimensions or use :doc:`global filters "
"<global_filters>` to offset the date and create pivot tables that compare "
"the current period's data with a previous period."
msgstr ""
"透過樞紐分析表的屬性複製樞紐分析表會建立額外的資料來源。這樣就能在同一個試算"
"表中對相同資料執行不同的操作。例如，您可以檢視依不同維度彙總的相同資料，或使"
"用\\ :doc:`全域篩選器 <global_filters>`\\ 來位移日期並建立樞紐分析表，以便比"
"較目前期間資料與先前期間資料。"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/spreadsheet/work_with_data/pivot_tables.rst:495
msgid "To duplicate a pivot table:"
msgstr "若要複製樞紐分析表："

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/spreadsheet/work_with_data/pivot_tables.rst:497
msgid ""
"With the :ref:`pivot table properties <spreadsheet/pivot-tables/properties>` "
"open, click the :icon:`fa-cog` :guilabel:`(gear)` icon then :icon:`fa-"
"clone` :guilabel:`Duplicate`."
msgstr ""
"開啟\\ :ref:`樞紐分析表屬性 <spreadsheet/pivot-tables/properties>`\\ 後，按一"
"下\\ :icon:`fa-cog`\\ :guilabel:`齒輪`\\ 圖示，然後按一下\\ :icon:`fa-"
"clone`\\ :guilabel:`複製`\\ 。"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/spreadsheet/work_with_data/pivot_tables.rst:500
msgid ""
"The duplicated pivot table is automatically inserted into a new sheet in the "
"spreadsheet, with the pivot table properties open in the right panel."
msgstr ""
"複製的樞紐分析表會自動插入試算表的新工作表中，樞紐分析表屬性在右側面板中開"
"啟。"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/spreadsheet/work_with_data/pivot_tables.rst:503
msgid ""
"Edit the :guilabel:`Name` in the properties panel and the sheet tab if "
"needed."
msgstr "如需要，請在屬性面板和工作表分頁中編輯\\ :guilabel:`名稱`。"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/spreadsheet/work_with_data/pivot_tables.rst:505
msgid ""
"The new data source is assigned the next available :ref:`pivot table ID "
"<spreadsheet/pivot-tables/properties-id>`. For example, if no other pivot "
"tables have been inserted in the meantime, duplicating *Pivot #1* results in "
"the creation of *Pivot #2*."
msgstr ""
"新資料來源會被指派下一個可用的\\ :ref:`樞紐分析表 ID <spreadsheet/pivot-"
"tables/properties-id>`\\ 。例如，如果在此期間尚未插入其他樞紐分析表，複製 "
"*Pivot #1* 會導致建立 *Pivot #2*。"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/spreadsheet/work_with_data/pivot_tables.rst:510
msgid ""
"Duplicating a pivot table by copying and pasting it or by duplicating the "
"sheet does not create a new data source. Any changes made to the pivot "
"table's properties would therefore impact any copies of the pivot table."
msgstr ""
"透過複製並貼上樞紐分析表或複製工作表來複製樞紐分析表不會建立新的資料來源。因"
"此，對樞紐分析表屬性所做的任何變更都會影響樞紐分析表的所有副本。"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/spreadsheet/work_with_data/pivot_tables.rst:513
msgid ""
"When a pivot table is duplicated, the new pivot table is, by default, "
"a :ref:`dynamic pivot table <spreadsheet/insert-pivot-table/static-vs-"
"dynamic>` whose dimensions and measures :ref:`can be manipulated "
"<spreadsheet/pivot-tables/build-manipulate>`."
msgstr ""
"複製樞紐分析表時，新樞紐分析表預設為\\ :ref:`動態樞紐分析表 <spreadsheet/"
"insert-pivot-table/static-vs-dynamic>`\\ ，其維度和量值\\ :ref:`可以操作 "
"<spreadsheet/pivot-tables/build-manipulate>`\\ 。"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/spreadsheet/work_with_data/pivot_tables.rst:520
msgid "Delete a pivot table"
msgstr "刪除樞紐分析表"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/spreadsheet/work_with_data/pivot_tables.rst:522
msgid ""
"To fully delete a pivot table and its data source from a spreadsheet, follow "
"these steps in any order:"
msgstr ""
"若要從試算表中完全刪除樞紐分析表及其資料來源，請依任意順序執行以下步驟："

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/spreadsheet/work_with_data/pivot_tables.rst:525
msgid ""
"Delete the pivot table using your preferred means, e.g., via keyboard "
"commands, spreadsheet menus, or by deleting the sheet."
msgstr ""
"使用您偏好的方式刪除樞紐分析表，例如透過鍵盤命令、試算表選單，或刪除工作表。"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/spreadsheet/work_with_data/pivot_tables.rst:527
msgid ""
"From the :ref:`properties panel <spreadsheet/pivot-tables/properties>` of "
"the relevant pivot table, click the :icon:`fa-cog` :guilabel:`(gear)` icon "
"then :icon:`fa-trash` :guilabel:`Delete`. This deletes the data source of "
"the pivot table."
msgstr ""
"從相關樞紐分析表的\\ :ref:`屬性面板 <spreadsheet/pivot-tables/properties>`\\ "
"中，按一下\\ :icon:`fa-cog`\\ :guilabel:`齒輪`\\ 圖示，然後按一下"
"\\ :icon:`fa-trash`\\ :guilabel:`刪除`\\ 。這將刪除樞紐分析表的資料來源。"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/spreadsheet/work_with_data/pivot_tables.rst:532
msgid ""
"Deleting the pivot table first results in a warning message beside the "
"corresponding data source in the :guilabel:`Data` menu, while deleting the "
"data source first results in a pivot table filled with :guilabel:`#ERROR` "
"errors."
msgstr ""
"先刪除樞紐分析表會在\\ :guilabel:`資料`\\ 選單中對應的資料來源旁顯示警告訊"
"息，而先刪除資料來源則會導致樞紐分析表充滿\\ :guilabel:`#ERROR`\\ 錯誤。"

